title: [FSX/P3D] FTX NA Southern California Quad
description:
FTX NA Southern California 

Quad installer for FSX, Prepar3D v1, Prepar3D v2, Prepar3D v3

Double-click on ftx_sca_100_p3dv3.reg to add a registration entry to your registry. Once the registration key has been added, use the quad installer to install the FTX Southern California scenery region
